{"tid":1924962,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"未停定開的士門嘔吐 醉女飛出車司機畀油走","createTime":"2020-03-14T04:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T08:30:30.000Z","uid":262673,"like":43,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e462fbce13e37bc3e284b08977d2b6d688191650","tid":1924962,"uid":262673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:48:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200314/HIJGOT7UZZ3CYBKOSQ7KLMP7KA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200314%2FHIJGOT7UZZ3CYBKOSQ7KLMP7KA%2F&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=bc69c531\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200314%2FHIJGOT7UZZ3CYBKOSQ7KLMP7KA%2F&h=9c0a5f06\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200314/HIJGOT7UZZ3CYBKOSQ7KLMP7KA/</a><br />\n<br />\n油麻地柯士甸道西與雅翔道交界橋底迴旋處，凌晨約2時半，一名約40歲醉酒女子乘的士駛經途中，疑不適想嘔吐。的士司機隨即減速，將車駛至一旁。現場消息指，的士未停定時，該女子已打開車門，結果不慎跌出車外，致左面額及雙膝擦傷；但司機未有協助，反而自行開車離去。<br />\n<br />\n有途人目擊事件，代為報警。女事主姓黃39歲，傷勢不太嚴重，但驚魂未定，稍後由到場救護員包紮，並由趕到的友人陪同送院。<br />\n<br />\n今次司機做得好，為求自保走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對付醉酒賴皮嘅醉酒婆，絕不手軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條女擅自開車門，抵佢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52af8d2de7b74d8ee1f878c1997ab0f3c3430819","tid":1924962,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:49:24.000Z","msg":"咁咪冇收到錢"},{"pid":"ff7dbdcc1ec6b3ad12efe1d9710407966ed8fc99","tid":1924962,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:50:52.000Z","msg":"40歲飲到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b2a2f5044254efe96a3332fca6505bc1db1166","tid":1924962,"uid":262673,"like":1,"dislik